title: Popcorn Time Community ( FIXED popcorntime.io(0.3.8-5) )
description:
Hey guys, this is a modified version of the original PopcornTime.io 0.3.8-5 that unfortunately stopped working.

This fix will change the torrent search APIs to working ones. You can find more information about it and thank those great people here:




DON'T FORGET to uninstall the old Popcorn Time from your computer before installing the new one. The steps for how to fix the old one without having to downloading it all again are in the Reddit page above.

HAVE FUN!
